body: "Context: runTest currently blocks obvious recursive test-all forms but misses global-flag-before-subcommand variants. Approach: strengthen command token parsing for pm, npx pm-cli, and node dist/cli.js forms, and add regression tests for add-time rejection plus runtime skip behavior."
